Title: Fail Fast on Concordion command ConcordionRunner->ConcordionRunner:runLeaf() ConcordionRunner->FixtureRunner:run() FixtureRunner->Concordion: process(fixture) Concordion->Specification:process() Specification->SpecificationCommand:execute() SpecificationCommand->CommandCall: getChildren().
processSequentially() CommandCall->ThrowableCatchingDecorator: execute() ThrowableCatchingDecorator->Command: execute() Note over Command: Assuming
command throws
exception Command-->ThrowableCatchingDecorator: throw Exception
ThrowableCatchingDecorator->ResultRecorder: record(EXCEPTION) ThrowableCatchingDecorator->ResultRecorder: recordFailFastException ThrowableCatchingDecorator-->SpecificationCommand: throw FailFastException FixtureRunner->ResultSummary: assertIsSatisfied(fixture) ResultSummary->FixtureState:assertIsSatisfied() FixtureState-->ConcordionRunner: throw new AssertionError
